et not to undermine Christians, Fayemi tells CAN In "News" Osun State Government has declared, Friday, 30th August 2019 public holiday to commemorate the Islamic New Year, Hijra 1441 AH. In "News" Osun Government has announced Tuesday as public holiday to commemorate the new Islamic year, 1440 after the Hijrah. In "News"